Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:50.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:51.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:52.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:52.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:53.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:58.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:08.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:22.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:27.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:32.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:34.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:38.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:45.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
